nodes.bodyText:
Building on the last thread, this is different from a switch statement on a single value.
        } else if (viewModel.isEmailProviderGmail()) {

That is a brand new boolean condition on the view model, the view should be able to know what to do based on a single value. In this case we have business logic in the view.
We should be able to get rid of all if statements and the method isEmailProviderGmail. The view should not be aware of a concept of 'gmail' or the different view providers, only that it gets data and it knows how to render it.

